@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Project Manager" as PM
participant ":System" as System

activate PM

PM -> System : Requests Core Flight DSL validation capability

activate System
System --> PM : Requests DSL file/content for validation
deactivate System

PM -> System : Provides DSL file/content

activate System
System --> System : Read DSL content
System --> System : Perform lexical analysis
System --> System : Perform syntactic analysis
System --> System : Build parse tree or AST
System --> System : Map AST to internal flight plan representation
System --> System : Perform semantic analysis

alt DSL content is valid
    System --> PM : Return valid flight plan representation
else DSL content is invalid
    System --> PM : Return meaningful validation errors
end

deactivate System
deactivate PM

@enduml